---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<section class="bg-[#fafaf2]">
  <div
    class="w-full flex min:h-[1536px] max-w-screen-xxl sm:mx-auto relative z-10 p-4 sm:p-6 lg:p-8 overflow-hidden bg-[#fafaf2] pb-6 sm:pb-10"
  >
    <div
      class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2 sm:gap-4 lg:gap-6 h-auto sm:h-[1536px]"
    >
      <div class="row-span-1 flex items-center justify-center p-2 sm:p-4">
        <Image
          src="/close-up.webp"
          class="object-cover rounded-lg"
          alt="A corner of our place"
          title="A corner of our place"
          width={600}
          height={400}
          quality={75}
          fetchpriority="high"
          loading="eager"
          sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 600px"
        />
      </div>
      <div
        class="row-span-1 flex flex-col justify-center px-4 sm:px-8 md:px-12 lg:px-16 py-4 sm:py-6 lg:py-8"
      >
        <h2
          class="mt-2 sm:mt-4 font-semibold text-base sm:text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl overflow-hidden"
        >
          Soul of the South
        </h2>
        <p
          class="mt-2 sm:mt-4 text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl xl:text-2xl overflow-hidden text-balance"
        >
          Where each <strong>dish</strong> is a tribute to tradition and
          <strong>local produce</strong>. Tapas that combine the flavor of
          immediacy with the depth of time, where simplicity and detail coexist
          in harmony.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="sm:hidden row-span-1 flex items-center justify-center p-2">
        <Image
          src="/salon-hzt.webp"
          class="object-cover rounded-lg"
          alt="Our dining room"
          title="Our dining room"
          width={600}
          height={400}
          quality={75}
          sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 600px"
        />
      </div>
      <div
        class="row-span-1 flex flex-col justify-center px-4 sm:px-8 md:px-12 lg:px-16 py-4 sm:py-6 lg:py-8"
      >
        <h2
          class="mt-2 sm:mt-4 font-semibold text-base sm:text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl overflow-hidden"
        >
          Raw Materials
        </h2>
        <p
          class="mt-2 sm:mt-4 text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl xl:text-2xl overflow-hidden text-balance"
        >
          <strong>Excellence</strong>, carefully selected from small producers,
          is the undisputed protagonist of each dish.<br /> A menu that follows the
          <strong>rhythm of the seasons</strong>, respecting each ingredient,
          <strong>without artifice</strong> or excess.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="hidden row-span-1 sm:flex items-center justify-center p-2 sm:p-4"
      >
        <Image
          src="/salon-hzt.webp"
          class="object-cover rounded-lg"
          alt="Our dining room"
          title="Our dining room"
          width={600}
          height={400}
          quality={75}
          sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 600px"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="row-span-1 flex items-center justify-center p-2 sm:p-4">
        <Image
          src="/mesa-hzt.webp"
          class="object-cover rounded-lg"
          alt="One of our tables"
          title="One of our tables"
          width={600}
          height={400}
          quality={75}
          sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 600px"
        />
      </div>
      <div
        class="row-span-1 flex flex-col justify-center px-4 sm:px-8 md:px-12 lg:px-16 py-4 sm:py-6 lg:py-8"
      >
        <h2
          class="mt-2 sm:mt-4 font-semibold text-base sm:text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl overflow-hidden"
        >
          For Everyone
        </h2>
        <p
          class="mt-2 sm:mt-4 text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl xl:text-2xl text-balance"
        >
          The new project by chef <strong>Borja Garc√≠a</strong>, <strong
            >Michelin Star</strong
          >, brings <strong>haute cuisine</strong> to all budgets in the heart of
          <strong>Puerto Real</strong>. <br /> An experience that celebrates
          <strong>Andalusian tradition</strong> with quality and authenticity. Enjoy
          a unique culinary experience, where each dish tells a story and each bite
          is a journey to the South.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
